54:00.336 --> 54:02.139
The vault.

54:04.756 --> 54:06.602
We're not alone.

54:08.191 --> 54:12.282
- Okay. Okay.
- I'm telling you the truth.

54:12.362 --> 54:14.434
Who's down there?

54:14.514 --> 54:17.396
No one goes down there, not even security...

54:19.015 --> 54:22.159
...because of what happened back in 1982.

54:22.239 --> 54:24.440
A man tried to rob the bank.

54:33.549 --> 54:35.818
<i>Someone got a line out.</i>

54:39.354 --> 54:43.592
