here, and they'll tell you the same.

57:01.730 --> 57:05.109
Something is still down there...

57:05.189 --> 57:08.830
...in the basement in the old bank.

57:15.676 --> 57:19.135
That was good. That was really good.

57:19.915 --> 57:22.137
