01:02:54.884 --> 01:02:56.706
No, they're not.

01:02:57.486 --> 01:02:59.576
No, they're not.

01:03:01.556 --> 01:03:03.424
No one's gonna die.

01:03:05.526 --> 01:03:07.395
Not even you.

01:03:43.064 --> 01:03:44.907
- What's their next move?
- I don't know.

01:03:44.987 --> 01:03:47.823
